Anyone else having trouble with the custom logo at 1:17:43 ? 
This code worked for me (so it maybe helps someone else too)

function config_custom_logo() {

    add_theme_support( 'custom-logo' );

}

add_action( 'after_setup_theme' , 'config_custom_logo' );

I found the easiest way to add class to the nav item is by using javascript dom manuplation
const navItem = document.querySelectorAll('.navbar-nav li');
navItem.forEach(item => {
  item.classList.add('nav-item');
  item.querySelector('a').classList.add('nav-link');
});

